= Skeletor

The Skeleton Application, contains example configuration for qcore and qcms.

== Configure

database.yml
sitemap.yml
settings.yml

== Bootstrap

rake qwerty:bootstrap

== Later

rake qwerty:cms:update_meta_definitions
rake qwerty:cms:update_sitemap_from_db

== Deployment

You need to create /public/uploads folder for FCKeditor image uploads

== Configure Development Tools

=== XRefresh

rake xrefresh:configure
rake xrefresh:run
Enable xrefresh panel in Firebug

== Notes

Versioning schema: http://semver.org